data.description: Welcome home to Snader's Summit, a new neighborhood in the heart of Carroll County.  This lovely new community in New Windsor is almost completely built out.  Conveniently located only 5 miles from Westminster.  Ward Communities builds luxury Townhomes with an open floor plan design.  This home has a gourmet kitchen, with a large island, and quartz countertops. This level has access to the large deck for more entertaining and relaxing. The top floor has 3 spacious bedrooms.  The primary suite in this model has vaulted ceilings, walk in closet, a second large closet and large primary bathroom.  Also on the top floor is your laundry.  The entry level has your garage entrance, a large flexible space to fit your needs,  (office, rec room, game room, extra bedroom) a full bathroom with shower and your door to the back yard. This neighborhood's reasonable HOA mows your yard also!! Welcome home.
